name: Monster Melodies
description: Join Groove Goblin as he teaches monsters the art of rock and roll! From eerie electric guitars to howling vocals, you'll learn to master the spookiest riffs and beats around!

name: Frankenstein's Funk Factory
description: Electrify your music skills at Frankenstein's Funk Factory! Assemble groovy melodies from scratch and learn the secrets to creating monstrous basslines that will have your audience dancing like creatures of the night.

name: Banshee Boogie Music Academy
description: At Banshee Boogie, you’ll scream with excitement as you learn to belt high-pitched vocals and eerie harmonies. Whether ghostly piano or haunted guitars, you’ll master music that’s truly out of this world!

name: The Yeti's Yodeling Institute
description: Climb the snowy peaks of sound with The Yeti! Learn the ancient monster art of yodeling, mastering powerful echoes that can shake mountains and melt ice with their monstrous melodies
